36.02	Brewster's_Millions_(1985_film)	Brewster's Millions (1985 film)	Brewster's Millions is a 1985 comedy film starring Richard Pryor and John Candy based on the 1902 novel of the same name by George Barr McCutcheon. It is the seventh film based on the story, with a screenplay by Herschel Weingrod &amp; Timothy Harris. It was directed by Walter Hill.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/5/5f/Brewsters_millions.jpg/220px-Brewsters_millions.jpg
